e included in this post, because they might become popular in the future. <em>Links checked: July/24 2008</em>.</p><h3>IT/Tech Job Boards: An Overview</h3><ul><li><a href="http://jobs.smashingmagazine.com">Smashing Jobs</a><br /> Our brand new board. Jobs that will smash into yur life. Job offerings for programmers and desiners.<br /> <a href="http://jobs.smashingmagazine.com"><img style="margin: 1em 0em 1em 4em" src="http://jobs.smashingmagazine.com/images/logo_jobs.jpg" alt="Logo Jobs in IT/Tech Job Boards" width="261" height="65" /></a></li><li><a href="http://jobs.37signals.com/jobs">37signals Job Board </a><br /> Companies such as The New York Times, CNET, Facebook, Adobe, Trek, and American Express use this Job Board to reach today&#8217;s best and brightest web minds.<br /> <a href="http://jobs.37signals.com/jobs"><img style="margin: 1em 0em 1em 4em" src="http://media.smashingmagazine.com/cdn_smash/images/job-boards/job-boards-00.jpg" alt="Job-boards-00 in IT/Tech Job Boards" width="268" height="103" /></a></li><li><a href="http://about.com/careers/">About &#8211; Jobs &amp; Careers</a><br /> Research job opportunities around the country, find salary mediums for different industries, and get practical, actionable advice on resume-writing and interview skills to help you land your dream job.<br /> <a href="http://about.com/careers/"><img style="margin: 1em 0em 1em 4em" src="http://media.smashingmagazine.com/cdn_smash/images/job-boards/job-boards-01.jpg" alt="Job-boards-01 in IT/Tech Job Boards" width="268" height="103" /></a></li><li><a href="http://aigaaustin.org/resources/jobs/">AIGA Austin &#8211; Jobboard</a><br /> This job bank is provided as a free service to the community.<br /> <a href="http://aigaaustin.org/resources/jobs/"><img style="margin: 1em 0em 1em 4em" src="http://media.smashingmagazine.com/cdn_smash/images/job-boards/job-boards-02.jpg" alt="Job-boards-02 in IT/Tech Job Boards" width="268" height="103" /></a></li><li><a href="http://www.authenticjobs.com/">Authentic Jobs &#8211; Cameron Moll</a><br /> Authentic Jobs is a targeted destination for standards-aware designers and developers and the companies seeking to hire them.<br /> <a href="http://www.authenticjobs.com/"><img style="margin: 1em 0em 1em 4em" src="http://media.smashingmagazine.com/cdn_smash/images/job-boards/job-boards-03.jpg" alt="Job-boards-03 in IT/Tech Job Boards" width="268" height="103" /></a></li><li><a href="http://bostonworks.boston.com/browse/jobs/web_developer.shtml">BostonWorks &#8211; Web Developer Jobs in Greater Boston</a><br /> Your source for job listings, job tools, networking events, career fairs and articles about finding the job you want in the Boston area.<br /> <a href="http://bostonworks.boston.com/browse/jobs/web_developer.shtml"><img style="margin: 1em 0em 1em 4em" src="http://media.smashingmagazine.com/cdn_smash/images/job-boards/job-boards-04.jpg" alt="Job-boards-04 in IT/Tech Job Boards" width="268" height="103" /></a></li><li><a href="https://careers.cnetnetworks.com/joblist.html?erpc=alljobs">CNET Networks | Jobs Career Page</a><br /> View a comprehensive list of available jobs.<br /> <a href="https://careers.cnetnetworks.com/joblist.html?erpc=alljobs"><img style="margin: 1em 0em 1em 4em" src="http://media.smashingmagazine.com/cdn_smash/images/job-boards/job-boards-05.jpg" alt="Job-boards-05 in IT/Tech Job Boards" width="268" height="103" /></a></li><li><a href="http://www.computerjobs.com/homepage.aspx">ComputerJobs.com</a><br /> Quickly locate Tech Jobs for IT professionals. Computer Jobs and Career Management Resources for Technology Professionals<br /> <a href="http://www.computerjobs.com/homepage.aspx"><img style="margin: 1em 0em 1em 4em" src="http://media.smashingmagazine.com/cdn_smash/images/job-boards/job-boards-06.jpg" alt="Job-boards-06 in IT/Tech Job Boards" width="268" height="103" /></a></li><li><a href="http://www.computingcareers.co.uk/job-roles/web-developer-jobs">Computing Careers</a><br /> Computing Careers has a large database of Web Developer jobs and progammer jobs, featuring hundreds of Web Developer vacancies posted by the top employers and recruiters in the IT industry.<br /> <a href="http://www.computingcareers.co.uk/job-roles/web-developer-jobs"><img style="margin: 1em 0em 1em 4em" src="http://media.smashingmagazine.com/cdn_smash/images/job-boards/job-boards-07.jpg" alt="Job-boards-07 in IT/Tech Job Boards" width="268" height="103" /></a></li><li><a href="http://sfbay.craigslist.org/">craigslist</a><br /> web/HTML/info design jobs, art/media/design jobs, internet engineering jobs, etc.<br /> <a href="http://sfbay.craigslist.org/"><img style="margin: 1em 0em 1em 4em" src="http://media.smashingmagazine.com/cdn_smash/images/job-boards/job-boards-08.jpg" alt="Job-boards-08 in IT/Tech Job Boards" width="268" height="103" /></a></li><li><a href="http://www.creativeheads.net/search.aspx">CreativeHeads.net</a><br /> Search for Creative Talent Jobs: Video Game Jobs, Animation Jobs, Visual Effects Jobs, TV &amp; Film Jobs, Software Jobs<br /> <a href="http://www.creativeheads.net/search.aspx"><img style="margin: 1em 0em 1em 4em" src="http://media.smashingmagazine.com/cdn_smash/images/job-boards/job-boards-09.jpg" alt="Job-boards-09 in IT/Tech Job Boards" width="268" height="103" /></a></li><li><a href="http://www.creativepool.co.uk/employee/jobboard.php">creativepool.co.uk</a><br /> creativepool.co.uk is the webs favourite place to find creative, design, media and web jobs in the UK. Browse hundreds of jobs in advertising, design, interiors, fashion, media, new media, print and publishing.<br /> <a href="http://www.creativepool.co.uk/employee/jobboard.php"><img style="margin: 1em 0em 1em 4em" src="http://media.smashingmagazine.com/cdn_smash/images/job-boards/job-boards-10.jpg" alt="Job-boards-10 in IT/Tech Job Boards" width="268" height="103" /></a></li><li><a href="http://www.crunchboard.com/">CrunchBoard</a><br /> The CrunchBoard job board gives you access to millions of technology and business savvy readers of TechCrunch, MobileCrunch, CrunchGear and other top technology blogs.. Use CrunchBoard to connect with the most dynamic programmers, designers, entrepreneurs, executives, venture capitalists and others who are deeply interested in the new web, and looking for their next career step.<br /> <a href="http://www.crunchboard.com/"><img style="margin: 1em 0em 1em 4em" src="http://media.smashingmagazine.com/cdn_smash/images/job-boards/job-boards-11.jpg" alt="Job-boards-11 in IT/Tech Job Boards" width="268" height="103" /></a></li><li><a href="http://www.daniweb.com/techtalkforums/forum72.html">DaniWeb Job Offers</a><br /> Web Development Job Offers, Software Development Job Offers, Internet Marketing Job Offers, Computer Tech / Consultant Job Offers<br /> <a href="http://www.daniweb.com/techtalkforums/forum72.html"><img style="margin: 1em 0em 1em 4em" src="http://media.smashingmagazine.com/cdn_smash/images/job-boards/job-boards-13.jpg" alt="Job-boards-13 in IT/Tech Job Boards" width="268" height="103" /></a></li><li><a href="http://www.devbistro.com/jobs">Dev Bistro</a><br /> Tech Jobs, web developer jobs, web design jobs, programming jobs<br /> <a href="http://www.devbistro.com/jobs"><img style="margin: 1em 0em 1em 4em" src="http://media.smashingmagazine.com/cdn_smash/images/job-boards/job-boards-15.jpg" alt="Job-boards-15 in IT/Tech Job Boards" width="268" height="103" /></a></li><li><a href="http://www.developers.net/tech-jobs">developers.net</a><br /> Tech Jobs | Computer Jobs | IT Jobs .Are you looking for Bay Area computer Jobs? IT Jobs in NYC? Our American job bank is one of the best job search engines for high-tech employment<br /> <a href="http://www.developers.net/tech-jobs"><img style="margin: 1em 0em 1em 4em" src="http://media.smashingmagazine.com/cdn_smash/images/job-boards/job-boards-16.jpg" alt="Job-boards-16 in IT/Tech Job Boards" width="268" height="103" /></a></li><li><a href="http://www.dice.com/